					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Notice that all objects in Super Mario Bros. are 16x16 pixels, made of a 2x2 block of 8x8 pixel tiles. These blocks are metatiles. Have a look through the <a href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/Glossary#M" class="postlink">nesdev.com glossary</a>.</div>

